{"tid":248284,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係怕左依家d男人！","createTime":"2017-05-18T12:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T12:36:57.000Z","uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f48f671bcc0cf225add51595a8e8649e4d2e231","tid":248284,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:33:43.000Z","msg":"我公司10幾人，9成係男人， <br />\n返工第一個星期就俾個已婚40幾歲男同事睇中仲經常借d椅約我lunch同dinner<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (我只同佢lunch過) <br />\n同佢wtsapp公事又講好多噯味野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我覺得越黎越唔對路，疏遠佢佢就咬住我唔放 <br />\n不停問我咩事唔彩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我忍無可忍 <br />\n有一次公司無人我同佢嘈交，我鬧到佢死之後佢終於唔再煩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整個過程困擾我長達3-4個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一單係上個月，個朋友介紹左個男仔俾我識，佢一見到我眼定定望住我， <br />\n我一見到佢我就知佢唔係我鍾意果type， <br />\n講開某d活動本來我地3個去，咁我唔鍾意人諗住做普通朋友，點知我個frd話唔得閒叫我地2個自己去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我呆一呆，到食完飯走時又叫佢送我搭車我已經勁唔鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個男仔又係咁問我係咪同佢出去，又係咁wtsapp我問，我無覆佢當無件事 <br />\n我以為唔覆佢應該知我對佢無意思，點知佢第日晚上打俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (我無聽) <br />\n果晚食完飯我同我朋友講左我唔想同個男仔來往，我依家覺得好困擾...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解依家d男人咁樣？？？令人覺得好恐怖....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec5c74bc5a8a627a6254fbf2cbe6108c6391478","tid":248284,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臭雞</span></span>"},{"pid":"c6f5a2a1378515a2faa6bc318872ab4e4128de00","tid":248284,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:34:58.000Z","msg":"Gay"},{"pid":"62fb60718fafa0db5eb8a4100f2039d3